abilities.name: Air Lock
abilities.description:
Blocks weather

If a weather effect takes place at the same timeslot, Air Lock will
completely negate it, as long as it's not Hail, Sun, or Aurora,
and is not currently active.

abilities.name: Delta Stream
abilities.description:
Increases the tier for Dust
Storm and Hail making it 1 tier higher than the baseline. Server side only
